3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper proposes an alternative approach to super-resolution, which involves the use of AI techniques.
4. cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as the paper deals with the generation of high-quality images, which is a key problem in computer graphics.
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is another possible category as the paper deals with the problem of super-resolution, which is relevant to multimedia applications such as image and video processing.
